> I am a junior Journalism Major currently studying at the University of Nebraska-Lincoln. I plan to graduate in December of 2014 in hopes of pursuing a career with a focus on the outdoors, hunting, and fishing.



### Experience:
I recently completed a paid internship with NebraskaLand Magazine during the summer of 2013. I was able to have three articles published in the September 2013 issue of the publication working under Head Editor Jeff Kurrus.

### About Me:
I have lived in Lincoln, Nebraska my whole life. I enjoy hunting, fishing, camping, sports, music,reading, movies and writing.
